OL,3,CYouth violence in Birmingham will rise
OL,4,Cif cuts continue, community leader
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FA community leader from has told ITV
OL,8,FNews he is worried about the impact
OL,9,Fwill have on youth violence in the
OL,10,Fcity.
OL,12,FMohammed Zafran, also known as Zaf,
OL,13,Fbegan steering youngsters towards
OL,14,Fsport and education after his brother-
OL,15,Fin-law-was stabbed to death in 2010.
OL,17,FHe has so far worked with more than
OL,18,F42,000 young people in the city and
OL,19,Fsays an increasing amount are being
OL,20,Ftempted towards a life of crime.
