OL,3,CYouth violence in Birmingham will rise
OL,4,Cif cuts continue, community leader
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FHe said: "With all these youth centres
OL,8,Fbeing closed down, a lot of these
OL,9,Fpolice stations being shut, all these
OL,10,Fjob cuts, that's not helping.
OL,12,F"And our youngsters come up to us and
OL,13,Fthey are saying 'look if we leave
OL,14,Fthese criminal activities, what are we
OL,15,Fgoing to do?
OL,17,F"There's no jobs out there. We're
OL,18,Flucky we're fortunate we come to these
OL,19,Fkinds of places where they give us
OL,20,Ffree activities."
