OL,3,CYouth violence in Birmingham will rise
OL,4,Cif cuts continue, community leader
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"Look at that doctor, that guy who's
OL,8,Fstudied at university and become a
OL,9,Fdoctor or that accountant or that
OL,10,Flawyer or maybe that footballer. Try
OL,11,Fto follow them."
OL,13,FZaf was recently made Chair of
OL,14,FCrimestoppers' West Midlands Volunteer
OL,15,FCommittee.
OL,17,FThe charity says is helping to ensure
OL,18,Fyoung people have the confidence to
OL,19,Freport crimes anonymously without fear
OL,20,Fof retribution.
